        <mxCell id="cEcDTE5n0xchJvEeUfNp-58" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fbf0e2;strokeColor=#d9822b;fontColor=#6a3c0e;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;spacingLeft=8;arcSize=4;" value="&lt;b&gt;Rigor rarely done for&lt;br&gt;low-resource sarcasm&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Bootstrap 95% CI&lt;br&gt;• McNemar + Bonferroni&lt;br&gt;• Calibration (ECE, T-scaling)&lt;br&gt;• Length-stratified error analysis&lt;br&gt;• Cross-dataset transfer&lt;br&gt;  (leakage-controlled)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Findings:&lt;/b&gt; gains significant vs&lt;br&gt;baselines; transfer is corpus-specific" vertex="1">
